07:45:32.459 --> 07:45:35.220
You are the hope of Pyre's future.

07:45:35.279 --> 07:45:38.400
You are the dragons who can bring lasting

07:45:38.400 --> 07:45:39.240
peace to this world.

07:45:39.299 --> 07:45:42.659
We wish you all the power of wings of

07:45:42.659 --> 07:45:42.959
fire.

