Students at Jade Mountain, Alba, Chiang

07:50:04.080 --> 07:50:07.259
Bai, Ermine, icicle, winter.

07:50:07.319 --> 07:50:10.319
Rain wings.

07:50:10.380 --> 07:50:11.759
